# Employee Attendance Management System

A simple and clean web application that allows employees to mark their daily attendance and allows managers to track and manage all attendance records. This project is built using **React + Vite**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Supabase**.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Features

### ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ’¼ Employee
- Register and log in.
- Check-in and check-out once per day.
- View personal attendance history.

### ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’¼ Manager
- Log in with manager access.
- View attendance of all employees.
- Filter by date or employee name.
- Track present, absent, or late status.

### âš™ï¸ General
- Secure authentication using Supabase Auth.
- Responsive UI (mobile + desktop).
- Fast development setup using Vite.

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, Vite, TypeScript
- **Database + Auth:** Supabase
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS
- **Package Manager:** npm (or Bun)
- **Version Control:** Git + GitHub

